cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image captioning models and bias in their predictions, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed model also involves machine learning techniques such as loss functions and probability calculations, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on gender-specific language in image captions, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) research.
